					<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content"><div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Christian religious education</div>
<style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r1033289096">.mw-parser-output .hatnote{font-style:italic}.mw-parser-output div.hatnote{padding-left:1.6em;margin-bottom:0.5em}.mw-parser-output .hatnote i{font-style:normal}.mw-parser-output .hatnote+link+.hatnote{margin-top:-0.5em}</style><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">For catechesis in the <a href="/wiki/Catholic_Church" title="Catholic Church">Catholic Church</a>, see <a href="/wiki/Catholic_catechesis" title="Catholic catechesis">Catholic catechesis</a>.</div>
<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1033289096"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">For the books, see <a href="/wiki/Catechisms" class="mw-redirect" title="Catechisms">Catechisms</a>.</div>
<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1033289096"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">"Catechumen" redirects here. For the video game, see <a href="/wiki/Catechumen_(video_game)" title="Catechumen (video game)">Catechumen (video game)</a>.</div>
<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1033289096"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">"Christian education" redirects here. For Christian educational institutions, see <a href="/wiki/Christian_school" title="Christian school">Christian school</a>.</div>
<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1033289096"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">Not to be confused with <a href="/wiki/Catachresis" title="Catachresis">catachresis</a>.</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">
